'''Guards (Burthorpe)''' are level 37 [[human]]s. A pair of [[Burthorpe]] guards flank either side of the main entrance to the [[Burthorpe Castle]]. They have average [[Defence]] and accuracy for their [[combat level]] and have a max hit of 5. Players occasionally train on these two guards for [[experience]] and their uncommon [[mithril platebody]] and [[mithril full helm]] drops.

